{"tid":1616871,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"真女警PHONE IN 港電反對禁幪面法","createTime":"2019-10-03T14:35:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T03:17:55.000Z","uid":299639,"like":219,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"b96397020fb008807ea35c3421c304fe1d936b18","tid":1616871,"uid":299639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:35:13.000Z","msg":"女警稱反對「禁蒙面法」 斥特首不應將警員「擺上枱」<br />\n2019-10-03 HKT 19:45<br />\n一名自稱是現職女便衣警員致電本台節目《自由風自由風》，表示自己反對訂立《禁蒙面法》，認為立法只會對現時情況火上加油，又批評特首林鄭月娥應解決政治問題，不要再將警員「擺上枱」。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，自己入職約4年半，對於近月有市民在遊行期間被警員所傷，她感到傷心，又說不明白同袍為何要這樣做。她又指，自己在這幾個月，由於身分不便公開，因此一直有蒙面參與遊行，並對一直以來願意說真話的議員、傳媒及社會人士致敬。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484084-20191003.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484084-20191003.htm&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEjQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=0807b007\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484084-20191003.htm&h=6bc127e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484084-20191003.htm</a><br />\nRespect!!!!"},{"pid":"07d493c519a99e0b321a49dbca81fbf795eb4aee","tid":1616871,"uid":299639,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:35:26.000Z","msg":"自推10下"},{"pid":"3287e5660d65c261453e027138da88241a8cd4e1","tid":1616871,"uid":299639,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:35:37.000Z","msg":"自推9下"},{"pid":"fff8af95865c5e9ed9b9b6d23d97289f7e600244","tid":1616871,"uid":299639,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:35:48.000Z","msg":"自推8下"},{"pid":"5bdc4bb250dd4930418873207544852beb6a7f85","tid":1616871,"uid":299639,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:36:00.000Z","msg":"自推7下"},{"pid":"be7d541f7f12be9beb40aac4169936ac2af7c62c","tid":1616871,"uid":299639,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"repl